      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $u,v \\in \\C$.\n    Montrer que $|u+v| + |u-v| \\ge |u| + |v|$, et d{\\'e}terminer les cas d'{\\'e}galit{\\'e}.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u,v \\in \\C\\)</span>. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(|u+v| + |u-v| \\ge |u| + |v|\\)</span>, et d<span>é</span>terminer les cas d’<span>é</span>galit<span>é</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e138ceb5-0a22-4e20-8887-8ae4bde2131e",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$|u+v| + |u-v| \\ge 2|u|$ et\n             $|u+v| + |u-v| \\ge 2|v|$. Il y a {\\'e}galit{\\'e} ssi $u = \\pm v$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(|u+v| + |u-v| \\ge 2|u|\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(|u+v| + |u-v| \\ge 2|v|\\)</span>. Il y a <span>é</span>galit<span>é</span> ssi <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u = \\pm v\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c4f6cd82-0ef0-4b43-973f-b9e042580b5d",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $z_1,z_2,z_3,z_4 \\in \\C$. Montrer que\n    $\\sum_{k=1}^4|z_k| \\le \\sum_{k=1}^3\\sum_{\\ell=k+1}^4 |z_k+z_\\ell|$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(z_1,z_2,z_3,z_4 \\in \\C\\)</span>. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{k=1}^4|z_k| \\le \\sum_{k=1}^3\\sum_{\\ell=k+1}^4 |z_k+z_\\ell|\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
